{"tid":1106183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到有個傻仔跌咗銀包","createTime":"2019-04-14T12:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T13:21:53.000Z","uid":5131,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aa169f5e66fcbe95961ad140cb19b601960e785c","tid":1106183,"uid":5131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:04:31.000Z","msg":"我攞左入面啲錢，跟住扔左落垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇錯我就係個傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下晝六點半喺天水圍天恆邨行去天澤商場條路<br />\n當時我攞住個爛咗少少既紙袋 入面裝住件返工衫同銀包<br />\n個陣我好急尿 所以跑左去商場 <br />\n未跑到商場我見到件衫跌左 我已經即刻執返起件衫<br />\n但發現冇左個銀包 然後即刻沿路搵 但已經搵唔返<br />\n如果有好心人執到可以tg我 <a href=\"https://t.me/iamon9boyy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fiamon9boyy&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=defbb6b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/iamon9boyy</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟仲係學生 今日岩岩出糧 入面有千3現金 好多相同證件<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知自己好on9將個銀包放係個爛左既紙袋到 大家鬧我當幫我推post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後比張銀包示意圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iODhvhH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiODhvhH.png&h=afb37cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再深藍少少"},{"pid":"9652f6b1ce8985974518fdf515cfaf1cab326b41","tid":1106183,"uid":53122,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:09:53.000Z","msg":"天水圍d垃圾地方<br />\n渣都無<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 天水圍窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f5690402bf960e0a7a14e8b4f82674c98bb598","tid":1106183,"uid":6156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1337d11eb2d9db68bd311bd25514fd2743d3c1ea","tid":1106183,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"一定搵唔到啦<br />\n天水圍呢啲地方"},{"pid":"537a59eb8013590acb489531854664f48af811b3","tid":1106183,"uid":5131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1337d11eb2d9db68bd311bd25514fd2743d3c1ea","tid":1106183,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"一定搵唔到啦<br />\n天水圍呢啲地方"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:31:04.000Z","msg":"我都預咗有呢個打算 只希望有人見到執咗打算玩返俾我"},{"pid":"234fc412744b37242535e8ddee55872db2602332","tid":1106183,"uid":6156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:31:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42138d0c3aef1de7ca9bf15374df348d4f8c58b5","tid":1106183,"uid":5131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T12:32:37.000Z","msg":"偏偏就係最急尿嘅時候 唔記得咗自己用緊一個穿咗嘅袋"},{"pid":"a503986e9e20bad648e8f0ad96a85344fc4c09dc","tid":1106183,"uid":5131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:02:31.000Z","msg":"個銀包有人還返俾我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7a5262e8614fbc8ef1d414de8b0888e916df1a","tid":1106183,"uid":122558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:20:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"379022783c79b9ec4a08c2bf3bf8c804ffeed5a7","tid":1106183,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a503986e9e20bad648e8f0ad96a85344fc4c09dc","tid":1106183,"uid":5131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:02:31.000Z","msg":"個銀包有人還返俾我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:21:53.000Z","msg":"你一定係靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}